    "Yang et al. (2020) focus on the application of RL and DRL techniques to sustainable energy and electric systems, addressing issues such as optimization, control, energy markets, cyber security, and electric vehicle management.",
    "In the realm of transportation systems, Li et al. (2023) explore various topics, including cooperative mobility-on-demand systems, driver assistance systems, autonomous vehicles (AVs), and electric vehicles (EVs).",
